Hong Kong to Keep ‘Close Watch’ on Short-Selling, K.C. Chan Says

-- B y   F o x   H u
-- 
2011-10-06T01:57:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/hong-kong-to-keep-close-watch-on-short-selling-k-c-chan-says.html
The Hong Kong government will
continue to keep a “close watch” on short-selling of
securities, K.C. Chan, secretary for financial services and the
Treasury, said today.  “Shorting activities are so far relatively normal,” Chan
said at the listing ceremony of Citic Securities Co.  To contact the reporter on this story:
